Almirall, Lundbeck Sign Accord To Market Antidepressant in Italy

-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 
2011-10-19T06:41:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/almirall-lundbeck-sign-accord-to-market-antidepressant-in-italy.html
  Almirall SA (ALM)  signed an accord with
H. Lundbeck A/S to market the antidepressant escitalopram in
 Italy , the Barcelona-based company said in a regulatory filing
today. Almirall expects to get revenue as soon as this year from
the treatment, to be sold under the brand Cipralex, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Manuel Baigorri at 
 mbaigorri@bloomberg.net  